SampleTeamClent
public abstract class TeamClient
extends BaseClient

An abstract PC2 Team Client that uses BaseClient

This Class contains all the "handle" methods required to implement a Team Client. Instead of figuring out which handle methods need to be used from BaseClient, this class has been used to create the PC2 Team Client.

Prerequisites:
- Extend this class
- Create Team accounts on admin

Important details:
- Remember to use loggoffPC2() before exiting

See Also:
BaseClient, Serialized Form

handleSettingsUpdated

public abstract void handleSettingsUpdated()
Description copied from class: BaseClient
Indicates when contest settings have changed

When contest settings are changed, this method is called. Contest settings include problem info, language info, account info and other contest settings.

Should be overridden by every Client.
